    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in mint condition and presents as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, consistent shine and no imperfections, while the interior is immaculate, featuring pristine upholstery and all original features in perfect working order. Mechanically, the car is sound, having been meticulously maintained with a complete service history. A buyer can expect a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives like new.",
