    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a distinguished pre-owned vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. This well-appointed unit has been curated for the discerning driver who prioritizes consistent performance and a refined cabin environment. Meticulously maintained and subjected to a rigorous evaluation, it offers an exceptional value proposition within its class. Experience a seamless fusion of sophistication and reliability in this expertly prepared offering.",
      "price": 29850.0,
